[[Dosiye:Flag of the Democratic Republic of the Congo.svg|center|thumb|Flag of the Democratic Republic of the Congo]]
N’ubwo Abatwa bavuga i[[kinyarwanda]] nk’[[abahutu]] n’[[abatutsi]], banenwa n’abandi baturage nkaho ntacyo bavuze. Abatwa ni 3% y’abaturage b’uRwanda kandi bakaba bafite uruhare ruto cyane muri [[politiki]] y’igihugu.<ref>[http://www.kituochakatiba.org/index2.php?option=com_docman&task=doc_view&gid=1199&Itemid=36 Ugushakisha Ukuri n’Ubumuntu, Kituo Cha Katiba, Nyakanga, 2012 – Gashyantare, 2013] </ref> 

